Accessorial Recommendation Agent – POC Build
Context
FreightPOP is a SaaS Transportation Management System (TMS).
When users create LTL shipments, they must select accessorials such as:
Liftgate
Residential Delivery
Limited Access
These are frequently missed at shipment creation time.
When carriers later invoice these accessorials:
The shipper absorbs unexpected cost
Or rebills customers months later (poor experience)
This leads to margin erosion, invoice disputes, and customer dissatisfaction.
The Assignment
You are the AI Product Manager responsible for designing and delivering a lightweight Proof of Concept (POC) for an Accessorial Recommendation Agent.
Your solution must:
Accept shipment inputs (address, shipment type, package type, etc.)
Return:
Suggested accessorial(s)
Confidence score
Short explanation
Include guardrails
Include an evaluation framework
Be cost-aware and performance-aware
Be safe for incremental rollout
This is not a slide deck exercise.
You must build a working prototype.
What You Must Deliver
